snippet.title: Sea Chronicles - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
SEA CHRONICLES
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2347290/Sea_Chronicles/

Sea Chronicles - is a first person comedy-adventure game where you're lost at sea. You try to find a way back home, but start to notice that you might not be alone on the ship. Is someone sabotaging your escape, or are you going insane?

===============================================================================

Expected Release Date : 2024
THE GAME IS STILL IN EARLY DEVELOPMENT, SOME GAMEPLAY FEATURES OR VISUALS MAY CHANGE

===============================================================================

Music: "Don't Forget to Groove" by Brian Claxton
